		<td><b>Ayla <span class="posthilit">sprite</span> demo: overlap sprites for more colors</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Simple demo I did very long ago (2004) which shows how to use 2 <span class="posthilit">sprite</span> layers on a NES to have sprites that looks like SNES, in this case, Ayla from Chrono Trigger.<br />No source.

		
