	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Has anyone tried instead of overlapping sprites - a <span class="posthilit">sprite</span> and a flickering &quot;mask&quot; <span class="posthilit">sprite</span> for half-tone effects?<br /><br />Wouldn't that give some of the benefits of 2 <span class="posthilit">sprite</span> layers but reduce unintentional flicker?

		

		</td>
