	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Ayla is a classic, fantastic demo!<br /><br />Almost everyone here on Nesdev seems to hate flickering - but I still think it's an amazing way to add more colors to NES graphics. I create new images using this technique everyday and my latest tests have less noticeable flickering.<br />I guess flickering results can be very good or disastrous - it all depends on how it's done.<br /><br />&quot;All unanimity is stupid&quot; - Nelson Rodrigues<br /><br /><img src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2TV9al2-NB0/ULjdJBOfJwI/AAAAAAAAAUk/QvtWaaHGeeE/s1600/072.png" alt="Image" />

		
